        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "This value must be in bytes and a multiple of 4KB.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "To change the stack size, you must set this property before starting your thread. Setting the stack size after the thread has started changes the attribute size (which is reflected by the ",
